Company Overview of Radiant Logistics, Inc.



SnapshotPeople 




OverviewBoard MembersCommittees



Executive Profile
E. Joseph Bento  Senior Vice President and Chief Operating Officer of Freight Forwarding Operations , Radiant Logistics, Inc.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 0 Board Members in 0 different organizations across 5 different industries.54--
Background

		Mr. E. Joseph Bento, also known as Joe, has been Chief Operating Officer of Freight Forwarding Operations at Radiant Logistics, Inc since June 30, 2016 and serves as its Senior Vice President. Mr. Bento served as Senior Vice President of Operations at Radiant Logistics, Inc. since January 5, 2016 until June 30, 2016. Mr. Bento served as President of North America and Chief Marketing Officer at CEVA Freight, LLC (formerly EGL Inc.) since July 2002 and September 2000 respectively. ... He served as Chief Sales Officer at SEKO Worldwide, LLC. He joined EGL Inc. in February 1992 as an Account Executive. He served as President of Americas & Global Freight Management at CEVA Holdings LLC. since August 2007. He served as Member of Executive Management Board at CEVA Holdings LLC until January 10, 2010. From March 1994 to December 1994, Mr. Bento served as Sales Manager in Los Angeles for EGL, and its Regional Sales Manager - West Coast from January 1995 to September 1997. From June 1994 to May 1995, he served as Station Manager in Los Angeles at EGL Inc. He served as Executive Vice President of Sales and Marketing of EGL from March 1999 to August 2000 and its Vice President of Sales and Marketing from October 1997 to February 1999. Mr. Bento holds a BS in Financial Management from California State University, Long Beach.Read Full Background




