        Bento boxes are a unique and stylish—yet simple—way to pack a waste-free lunch. In bento lunch boxes, every part of your meal can be compactly and neatly stowed, allowing you and your family to pack a zero-waste lunch in one convenient, self-contained space. In fact, the word “bento” is a slang term from the Song dynasty that means convenient! Each bento box you’ll find here features helpful dividers and small containers to keep food separate, fresh and uncontaminated. Choose your color, size, style and material—and let our kids bento boxes and bento boxes for adults organize your waste-free lunch and lifestyle.    

